Kb3 Ke5 68. Bc8 Kf6 69. Kc2 Ke5 70. Kd3 $11) 67. Ka4 {[#]} Ke5 68. Kb5 c3 69.
Bb3 Bd4 70. Bc2 Kd6 71. Kc4 Ke5 72. f6 1-0

